nd tenure track faculty in thirteen top us research universities dual career academic couples explores the impact of dual career partnering on hiring retention professional attitudes and work culture in the us university sector it also makes recommendations for improving the way universities work with dual career candidates and strengthen overall communication with their faculty on hiring and retention issues please click on the link below to download pdf files of the full report including executive summary there is no charge for this report full report dual career academic couples what universities need to know august 2008 donate make a donation social links facebook twitter youtube scribd contact serra house 589 capistrano way stanford ca 94305 8640 map 650 723 1994 gender email stanford edu
